    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The base game includes vehicles for ALL classes! Screenshots include user generated content and DLC content.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bounty Drag Racing: Drag Racing Evolved is the most complete online-only drag racing experience on the market.  Race the fastest and most varied types of dragsters in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fine tune your cars to achieve maximum performance in a constantly changing weather and get online for the most competitive drag racing encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CURRENTLY COMPATIBLE WITH: Logitech, Thrustmaster, and Most Fanatec Wheels. Moza wheels are currently NOT compatible.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The most complete drag racing experience including track racing, street racing, and sand drag racing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Decide where YOU want to start, anywhere from a bracket car to a 5 second Dragster</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*In depth tuning system with power adder tuning</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*True to life staging system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Radial Tire suspension tuning</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Live Engine Swap System allows you to change engine while at the track</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Featuring 4 Cylinder, 6 Cylinder, 8 Cylinder, 2 rotor, 3 rotor, 4 rotor, and diesel engines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Dynamic Weather System that affects car performance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Monthly Competitive Events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Detailed interiors and engines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*More cars and tracks added regularly</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/06f535fc96d6db7bb0b7294faa7b23b3.poster.avif?t=1768617156\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/06f535fc96d6db7bb0b7294faa7b23b3.webm?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/06f535fc96d6db7bb0b7294faa7b23b3.mp4?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/153249cc0caa7dc9921d0f45677566da.poster.avif?t=1768617156\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/153249cc0caa7dc9921d0f45677566da.webm?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/153249cc0caa7dc9921d0f45677566da.mp4?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/a2daff4f570b4ea578dc77e1f098f6dd.poster.avif?t=1768617156\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/a2daff4f570b4ea578dc77e1f098f6dd.webm?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/a2daff4f570b4ea578dc77e1f098f6dd.mp4?t=1768617156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803390/extras/f15f242bd812c82e20d1ae36cccfc3e5.poster.avif?t=1768617156\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset